dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. North oriented to the leftof the map. Includes a decorative cartouche with grapes and vines, compass rose, and illustrations of ships on the ocean. From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 38 x 49 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_title_s: Bourdelois, pays de Medoc, et la prevoste de Born.; Bovrdelois, pays de Medoc, et la prevoste de Born.
